1
00:00:26,400 --> 00:00:28,440
Put out the fire in the furnace.

2
00:00:28,960 --> 00:00:31,720
Let's test the medicine later. It cannot be put out.

3
00:00:31,720 --> 00:00:32,520
Why?

4
00:00:32,520 --> 00:00:34,520
Just like making the best dough

5
00:00:34,520 --> 00:00:35,600
requires the use of sourdough,

6
00:00:35,600 --> 00:00:37,160
to make a perfect pill,

7
00:00:37,160 --> 00:00:38,760
you have to use an old fire.

8
00:00:39,040 --> 00:00:41,000
The more powerful the pill,

9
00:00:41,000 --> 00:00:42,240
the more you need to use an old fire.

10
00:00:42,240 --> 00:00:43,320
I have been making pills for decades,

11
00:00:43,320 --> 00:00:46,040
and I have never heard of such a thing.

12
00:00:46,040 --> 00:00:49,040
Who understands the alchemy classics better, you or me?

13
00:00:49,040 --> 00:00:51,040
If you don't believe me, put it out.

14
00:00:51,320 --> 00:00:53,040
But if the pill doesn't work,

15
00:00:53,040 --> 00:00:54,040
don't blame me.

16
00:00:56,400 --> 00:00:57,680
Suit yourself.

17
00:01:00,840 --> 00:01:02,520
Once taken,

18
00:01:02,520 --> 00:01:04,200
it grants boundless strength.

19
00:01:04,200 --> 00:01:07,130
The invulnerable golden elixir is finally refined.

20
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,920
Someone broke in.

21
00:01:17,760 --> 00:01:18,600
Ayun.

22
00:01:21,360 --> 00:01:22,200
Ayun.

23
00:01:23,280 --> 00:01:24,039
Ayun.

24
00:01:24,039 --> 00:01:24,880
Even if I die,

25
00:01:25,280 --> 00:01:26,560
I will save you.

26
00:01:28,160 --> 00:01:30,080
Those who block me will die.

27
00:01:33,720 --> 00:01:36,479
Mo Yu, catch!

28
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:46,600
I knew you were secretly refining the golden elixir.

29
00:01:46,600 --> 00:01:47,400
General,

30
00:01:47,400 --> 00:01:49,080
I found that Mu Jiuyun secretly hoarded medicinal materials.

31
00:01:49,080 --> 00:01:50,920
I know all of this.

32
00:01:50,920 --> 00:01:52,120
Don't alert her for now.

33
00:01:52,120 --> 00:01:53,720
I want to see

34
00:01:54,039 --> 00:01:56,840
what she uses the hidden medicinal materials for.

35
00:02:04,600 --> 00:02:07,400
There is indeed something in the alchemy furnace.

36
00:02:08,160 --> 00:02:09,880
Once swallowed,

37
00:02:09,880 --> 00:02:11,440
you can become incredibly strong.

38
00:02:11,440 --> 00:02:16,370
The invincible golden elixir that makes one invulnerable to swords is finally refined.

39
00:02:18,960 --> 00:02:22,480
Before, I was afraid you would tamper with the golden elixir.

40
00:02:22,480 --> 00:02:23,720
Now that I've seen

41
00:02:23,720 --> 00:02:26,250
you throw the golden elixir directly to Mo Yu,

42
00:02:26,280 --> 00:02:30,800
it seems my worry was unnecessary.

43
00:02:42,240 --> 00:02:44,280
This pill is indeed miraculous.

44
00:03:11,400 --> 00:03:12,280
A'yun.

45
00:03:39,480 --> 00:03:40,440
Su Cheng.

46
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:41,960
Su Cheng.

47
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:48,760
Mo Yu.

48
00:03:50,800 --> 00:03:52,280
Su Cheng, are you alright?

49
00:03:55,960 --> 00:03:58,020
If he can risk his life to protect you,

50
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,960
I naturally can too.

51
00:04:05,680 --> 00:04:06,840
Jiuyun,

52
00:04:09,280 --> 00:04:10,640
don't forget me.

53
00:04:25,760 --> 00:04:26,840
Su Cheng.

54
00:04:28,160 --> 00:04:29,080
Su Cheng.

55
00:04:30,720 --> 00:04:33,120
Like birds flying wing to wing in the sky.

56
00:04:33,120 --> 00:04:35,200
Like flounders in water, we'll never part.

57
00:04:35,200 --> 00:04:36,880
You keep one piece, and I'll keep the other.

58
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:38,720
We will never be apart.

59
00:04:39,440 --> 00:04:40,200
Yeah.

60
00:04:47,680 --> 00:04:49,680
When the two jade pendants become one,

61
00:04:49,680 --> 00:04:51,120
you will be my bride.

62
00:04:54,360 --> 00:04:54,960
Yeah.

63
00:05:07,880 --> 00:05:08,760
Mo Di,

64
00:05:09,320 --> 00:05:10,520
do you have a heart?

65
00:05:11,560 --> 00:05:14,160
Although Su Cheng has no blood relation to you,

66
00:05:14,680 --> 00:05:17,040
you lived together for ten years.

67
00:05:17,720 --> 00:05:19,440
Don't you have any affection,

68
00:05:19,440 --> 00:05:20,720
or a shred of humanity?

69
00:05:20,720 --> 00:05:22,880
Only the weak talk about feelings.

70
00:05:23,480 --> 00:05:25,560
If you pity them so much,

71
00:05:25,560 --> 00:05:28,040
I'll send you to see them right now.

72
00:05:28,600 --> 00:05:29,880
If I die,

73
00:05:30,160 --> 00:05:31,960
you'll never get the Dan Manual.

74
00:05:33,400 --> 00:05:37,240
You are of no use to me anymore.

75
00:05:39,720 --> 00:05:40,680
Ah!

76
00:05:41,400 --> 00:05:43,640
What exactly did you put

77
00:05:43,640 --> 00:05:45,720
in the pills?

78
00:05:45,720 --> 00:05:47,560
We are both master alchemists.

79
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:50,320
Of course I know you can deduce the secret formula

80
00:05:50,320 --> 00:05:52,560
from the pills.

81
00:05:52,560 --> 00:05:54,090
If you get the alchemy book,

82
00:05:54,840 --> 00:05:56,480
I'm afraid I wouldn't escape death either.

83
00:05:56,480 --> 00:05:57,920
I didn't expect

84
00:05:58,840 --> 00:06:00,320
that I would be

85
00:06:01,120 --> 00:06:02,240
defeated

86
00:06:02,560 --> 00:06:04,560
by you today.

87
00:06:43,720 --> 00:06:44,640
Yun.

88
00:06:46,159 --> 00:06:47,960
Eat something and get some rest.

89
00:06:48,880 --> 00:06:50,120
I can't eat.

90
00:06:50,280 --> 00:06:52,760
You've been taking care of Su Cheng non-stop for two days.

91
00:06:52,760 --> 00:06:53,920
Let me take over.

92
00:06:56,000 --> 00:06:57,860
He became like this because of me.

93
00:06:58,080 --> 00:07:00,010
But it hurts me to see you like this.

94
00:07:02,000 --> 00:07:03,730
Su Cheng won't die that easily.

95
00:07:04,880 --> 00:07:06,520
If you still refuse to eat,

96
00:07:06,880 --> 00:07:08,880
I will go on a hunger strike with you.

97
00:07:24,640 --> 00:07:25,600
Let me do it.

98
00:07:53,800 --> 00:07:54,659
Zhong Xia Qiang

99
00:07:55,400 --> 00:07:55,760
Peng Yin

100
00:07:55,760 --> 00:07:57,040
Zijian Qiangqipin Pengyin

101
00:07:57,040 --> 00:07:57,360
Quan Xuhang

102
00:07:57,360 --> 00:07:58,020
Quan Xuhang

103
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,260
Quan Yulong

104
00:07:59,760 --> 00:08:00,560
Licheng Lefei

105
00:08:01,120 --> 00:08:01,520
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing

106
00:08:01,520 --> 00:08:03,120
Yunlong Yinyu Jiaguangjing

107
00:08:05,320 --> 00:08:05,680
Luoxiao Conglin Xunbo

108
